  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to gupnp</title>

    <para><application>GUPnP</application> is an elegant, object-oriented open source
    framework for creating UPnP devices and control points, written in C using GObject
    and libsoup.</para>

    &lfs70_built;

